Router 1 (R1) Configuration

enable
configure terminal
hostname R1
!
interface FastEthernet0/0
 description --- Connection to Switch1 (LAN 1) ---
 ip address 195.120.150.1 255.255.255.224
 no shutdown
exit
!
interface FastEthernet1/0
 description --- WAN Link to R2 ---
 ip address 195.120.150.33 255.255.255.224
 no shutdown
exit
!
end

Command Explanations:
	•	enable → Enters privileged mode
	•	configure terminal → Enters global configuration mode
	•	hostname R1 → Sets router name
	•	interface FastEthernet → Selects interface
	•	description → Adds interface description
	•	ip address → Assigns IP and subnet mask
	•	no shutdown → Activates interface
	•	exit → Returns to previous mode
	•	end → Exits to privileged mode


