Add Redistribution on R2

configure terminal

router ospf 1
 redistribute rip subnets

router rip
 redistribute ospf 1 metric 1

end


🧠 Command Explanations (OSPF)
	•	router ospf 1
→ Starts OSPF process with ID 1
	•	network <network> <wildcard> area <id>
→ Advertises network into OSPF
→ Assigns interface to specific area
	•	0.0.0.31
→ Wildcard mask for /27 subnet


🔥 HOW DESIGN WORKS NOW
	•	R1 ↔ R2 → RIP
	•	R2 ↔ R3 → OSPF Area 0 (Backbone)
	•	R3 ↔ R4 → OSPF Area 1

👉 R3 becomes ABR (Area Border Router)


